[[Pɔɔ]] cɔlʋʋ kɛna tʋmɩyɛ nɖɩ palakɩ-ɖɩ [[lɩm]] taa kɛnɛ yɔ. Palakɩ-ɖɩ nɛ pakpaɣ lɩm taa tɛtɛ kpɩna. Ɖɩkpaɣ ɛzɩ [[Kpakpayaɣ|kpakpasɩ]] kɛ mbɩ yɔ. Ɛlɛ, lɩm taa peeɖe pagba lɩm taa kpɩna wena payan̄ɛ nɛ fransɩ kʋnʋŋ taa size "crustacés waa" nɛ "céphalopodes waa" yɔ.
